    ConnectionDialogController

    This class corresponds to the controller of the creationDialog
    Impression
    This class corresponds to the printing capabilities of our application
    ListenerButtonPanelLeft
    This class corresponds to the listener of the panel left (New connection, Refresh, Disconnection)
    ListenerButtonPanelRight
    This class corresponds to the different listener of the right panel (Create table, column, row...)
    ListenerMenu
    This class corresponds to the different listener of the menu bar as well as the JToolBar
    ListenerTableDataColumn

    ListenerTree
    This class corresponds to the listener of the tree, thanks to this tree will be transformed according to the tables, the views or the triggers added
